## 🛠️ Technical Debt & Improvement

| Area | Status Saat Ini | Rekomendasi |
|------|----------------|-------------|
| **Testing** | ❌ Tidak ada test | Tambahkan unit test + integration test (Jest/Vitest) |
| **Error Handling** | ⚠️ Dasar | Tambah error boundary global + Sentry logging |
| **Deployment** | ❌ Development only | Dockerize + CI/CD pipeline (GitHub Actions) |
| **Environment** | ⚠️ .env file | Proper secret management (Vault/AWS Secrets) |
| **File Storage** | ⚠️ Local disk | Migrasi ke cloud storage (S3) untuk scalability |
| **Database** | ⚠️ sync alter | Gunakan Sequelize migrations untuk production |
| **Caching** | ❌ Tidak ada | Redis cache untuk API response yang berat |
| **Logging** | ⚠️ console.log | Structured logging (Winston/Pino) |
| **Input Sanitization** | ⚠️ Dasar | Tambah XSS protection + SQL injection prevention |
| **API Documentation** | ❌ Tidak ada | Swagger/OpenAPI docs untuk semua endpoint |

